divs: Sighting Detailsin ref. case # 22092 I don't know if you know what you have but I beleive you have the smoking gun. This is the best pic yet. In the upper left hand of your photo is a black ops MH-47 chinook used in speceial operations. They are either following or chasing 3 bell shap objects. If I were you I would take security measures with this pic. They will want it. BE CAREFULL.
